current.body: International Students' Association (ISA) is a student group at the University of Alberta with the mission to serve, represent and advocate for the interests of the international students at the University of Alberta.
DishZero is a student group that provides students and staff with reusable alternatives to traditional disposable takeout containers and mugs.
Alzheimer Society of Calgary aims to enable local people impacted by dementia to live life well and build the capacity of the community to support and care for them.
